data.text:
The Exemplary Performance Recognition Project expands recognition of outstanding performers at the WSMA State Solo & Ensemble Festival. State festival adjudicators select the most exceptional performances at each of the festival campuses through a two step process.

Step 1. Throughout the festival day, adjudicators nominate events for the award.

Nominations are listed below.

Step 2. At the end of the festival day, the adjudicator selects up to two (2) award recipients from the nominated events in their festival site.

View the list of 2019 award recipients »

Congratulations to all the NOMINATED performances in 2019!

First weekend (April 27) all results are now posted.

Second weekend (May 3-4) all results are now posted.

May 22 festival results are now posted.
